{"tid":105536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"畸胎】女子誕古怪「青蛙嬰」 夭折後遭當眾燒屍","createTime":"2017-02-03T03:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T03:55:41.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24cfe9beeece4629515165ba82a97a905dccdcb3","tid":105536,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:29:07.000Z","msg":"迎接家庭新生命本來是一件開心事，但對津巴布韋一名婦人來說卻是地獄般的經歷。她懷胎八月誕下的「嬰孩」離奇細小下肢纖瘦，被形容「猶如青蛙的生物」，令眾人大感吃驚，更被下令當眾燒屍。<br />\n<br />\n戈奎（Gokwe）36歲女子尼亞蒂（Precious Nyathi）生下來的寶寶雙腿幼細彎曲，驟眼看就如青蛙的腿部。她表示：「我們想要一個孩子，這就是上天給我們的，這是地獄般的經歷，將會困擾我一生。」<br />\n<br />\n其39歲丈夫諾莫爾（Nomore）憶稱：「我趕回家卻驚見一隻青蛙&hellip;&hellip;是由我太太誕下的。醫院的人也確認太太已產子，他們同樣震驚。」<br />\n<br />\n夫婦倆把嬰兒帶到醫院，但不久後死亡，他們又把嬰屍帶回家，尋求村落長老發落，長老研究後要求他們當着村民面前燒屍。死嬰就被放在一張寫滿字的紙上，再放在地上準備燒毀。<br />\n<br />\n醫院指尼亞蒂有定期入院做檢查，但對她誕下「青蛙嬰」感到吃驚，暫時未知她誕下怪胎的原因。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n「猶如青蛙的生物」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486091652_c0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486091652_c0b3.jpg&h=8db86306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n36歲女子尼亞蒂（Precious Nyathi）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/small/1486091653_0cf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Fsmall%2F1486091653_0cf5.jpg&h=db23d93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170203/56253696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170203%2F56253696&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmNixMNwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=f32a7c68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170203%2F56253696&h=9bd1083d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170203/56253696</a>"},{"pid":"92bc810a40e90c2ad1f8c75f03de7b9651ebd17b","tid":105536,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"咁撚細隻 未生出黎望個肚唔大都知奶野喇"},{"pid":"fa41d41969628df1f3a5f5cce27a2d711f20b68a","tid":105536,"uid":28878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"似假新聞"},{"pid":"39288fe925b3b3b659f114a860f867d31ddc02d0","tid":105536,"uid":17776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:49:21.000Z","msg":"我痾舊屎都大過佢"},{"pid":"d36aaa2f914fa02adaa8f25bde43ad54fc7c67a2","tid":105536,"uid":52794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我痾舊屎都大過佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係咁話"},{"pid":"383fa26c3ec201ec77ad27cb6b3ed31ae0e4d9ba","tid":105536,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T03:55:41.000Z","msg":"屌呢隻真係青蛙黎喎師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條友比青蛙戴帽"}]}